modName: Katts Story Save File Level One
summary: Level one Nord woman, left abandoned,, you start level one, alternative beginning.  You will get a message to look into Helgen. Fight your way through the Abandoned Prison, have fun. No Cheats, you will find all that you need as you venture on.     SKSE needed, im assuming
descriptionHtml:
[IMG]http://i1055.photobucket.com/albums/s502/lycanheart/katt1_zpsfd660631.jpg[/IMG]
[IMG]http://i1055.photobucket.com/albums/s502/lycanheart/katt2_zpsaa40d906.jpg[/IMG]
Fight your way through the Abandoned Prison, I take no credit for this file, it\\\\\\\'s just a start i found intriguing, and thought i\\\\\\\'d share with you all. I just added the Female. 
[IMG]http://i1055.photobucket.com/albums/s502/lycanheart/att3_zpsc859b62b.jpg[/IMG]
I am using UNP body, 
This mod requires Random Alternate Start by Syclonixy   http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/25404,, what a wonderful mod. 
Face Shop - Face Texture Options in Race Menu by Natilde http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/27785
and  Ponytail Hairstyles by Azar  http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/31797 to get the right look. 
I used SKSE, this may be needed.


I apologies if this mod already exists or if somebody already had this in mind, I likes the playthrough and just wanted to share irt.
